OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fties to Chinese programme  
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A Harvard University professor has been
OL,6, convicted of hiding ties to a China-run
OL,7, recruitment programme.                 
OL,9,FCharles Lieber was found guilty of     
OL,10,Fmaking false statements to authorities,
OL,11,Ffiling false tax returns and failing to
OL,12,Freport a Chinese bank account. His     
OL,13,Fsentencing date is yet to be decided.  
OL,15,FThe 62-year-old was charged in 2020 as 
OL,16,Fpart of a US campaign to counter       
OL,17,Feconomic espionage from China.         
OL,19,FHowever, some critics say this campaign
OL,20,Fharms academic research.               
